{"tid":1300673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地要帶起一場hashtag感謝運動     eg寶礦力","createTime":"2019-07-09T12:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T14:38:44.000Z","uid":244210,"like":149,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"249d632f196ee6db842374111e2b471207e29bac","tid":1300673,"uid":244210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"為加強支持，並提供<span style=\"color: red;\">免費宣傳</span>比支持今次運動嘅唔同行業嘅公司，人物等(例如餐廳，youtuber，廣告商等)，我希望有IT bada可以整個list整合，放上網並keep住update，等市民可以容易見到咩product/餐廳支持運動而選擇消費<br />\n<br />\n例如最近寶礦力支持抵制tvb，我地add佢入list，大家買野可以傾向支持該產品，買完產品，影相並po ig/facebook hashtag #thxPocari <br />\n<br />\n餐廳，日常用品等如是，格式係 #thxZZZZ (ZZZZ係個品牌名)<br />\n<br />\nOnline list Details<br />\n。要有search功能，大家可以直接search<br />\n。最好有個hashtag建議，更統一，更容易成風<br />\n<br />\nSharing Details<br />\n。<span style=\"color: red;\">無買product都可以開post hashtag支持</span> (唔鼓勵用story)<br />\n。如果list整好，大家係post度寫埋條link，鼓勵其他人用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅IT bada可以tg我，我開group大家一齊搞掂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果成風，成果會好大，<span style=\"color: red;\">hashtag感謝運動</span>hashtag感謝運動搞唔搞得成靠大家啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第一炮，大家集火thx左寶礦力先! #thxPocari</span></span>"},{"pid":"30d9ec845768b27c2c6253f606e88350115f76b0","tid":1300673,"uid":263152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0cd36e056e53eecd7244302d0d60e4e2e1824d0d","tid":1300673,"uid":73948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d27815dda768b6c6dcf87e2aa14b7997869738f1","tid":1300673,"uid":244210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:24:55.000Z","msg":"#thxPocari"},{"pid":"6d0fe02fce0caf51a93b09eddf85efa6fe492795","tid":1300673,"uid":673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"p